org.opensourcedea.dea

Class DEAPSolution

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opensourcedea.dea.DEAPSolution
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DEAPSolution
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class defines a DEA Problem Solution. All the methods in this class are used to set or get part of a DEA Problem Solution (DEAPSolution).
    Author:
    Hubert Virtos
